Shore Capital Close to Adding 60% Stake in DBD, Telegraph Says

-- B y   K a r i   L u n d g r e n
-- 
2011-03-13T11:15:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-13/shore-capital-close-to-adding-60-stake-in-dbd-telegraph-says.html
Shore Capital Group Plc is close to
acquiring a majority stake in German telecoms company DBD
Deutsche Broadband Dienste, the Sunday Telegraph reported.  The U.K.-based investment bank has led a group of
investors, which may include a number of Israeli businessmen, to
take a close to 60 percent stake in DBD, the newspaper said,
without saying where it got its information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kari Lundgren in London at 
 klundgren2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:  Will Kennedy  at 
 wkennedy3@bloomberg.net . 